To copy from source: buffer of 4 i32 to destination: buffer of 4 i32.
Let i be 0.
While i is less than 4: destination at i becomes source at i; i becomes i plus 1.

To sum buffer cells: buffer of 4 i32, giving i32.
Let total be 0.
Let i be 0.
While i is less than 4: total becomes total plus cells at i; i becomes i plus 1.
Give total.

To main, giving i32.
Let source be buffer of 4 i32 filled with 3.
Let destination be buffer of 4 i32 filled with 0.
copy from source to destination.
Give sum buffer destination.
